OL,7,FPeople living off-grid, including in
OL,8,Fparks and on houseboats, are struggling
OL,9,Fto heat their homes as they wait to
OL,10,Freceive support payments through a
OL,11,Fdelayed Government scheme that was
OL,12,Ffirst promised in September last year.
OL,14,FOne pensioner living in a park home
OL,15,Ftold i she is too scared to put her
OL,16,Fheating on, while a boater said he is
OL,17,Fconcerned when he sees other houseboats
OL,18,F"without smoke coming out of the
OL,19,Fchimney".
OL,3,C'It's scary': People living off-grid
OL,4,Cfeel forgotten after delays to energy
OL,5,Cbill support
